sentence: In early trading on Friday, shares of Procter & Gamble ( PG ) topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 0.4%.
Year to date, Procter & Gamble registers a 3.6% gain.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Goldman Sachs Group ( GS ), trading down 2.8%.
Goldman Sachs Group is lower by about 14.1% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are JPMorgan Chase ( JPM ), trading down 2.6%, and Coca-Cola ( KO ), trading up 0.3% on the day.
